Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,館內已經發現敵人放置的爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人員請盡速前往防爆室避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離自爆裝置啟動前還有5分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.49,0:01:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，光是對付外面的敵人就已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是特洛伊木馬嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特特洛伊，特特洛伊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還無法解除啊真是笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個臭炸彈在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.77,0:02:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了讓我們迷惑焦慮而故意裝置的簡單陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以中計呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.61,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬頭，豬頭，豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒精，酒精，酒精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是想互淋啤酒應該不需要打火機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是零食店的簽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這玩意絕對不是那麼好玩的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順著這些管道前進的方塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到最下面的引爆裝置大概就會爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該錯不了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣擋下那些方塊不就行了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情沒有那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方塊上面有個節拍計時器不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這叫鐘擺引信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果隨便去動它讓它碰到旁邊的金屬的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個混蛋炸彈我要宰了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我不是說過了這只是簡單的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開卡車撞上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是危險又美麗啊，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個強力膠把所有方塊的計時器黏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓它們停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.11,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黏著計時器的方塊全都是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一某個被擋住而導致炸彈爆炸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩5分鐘而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，距離自爆裝置啟動只剩1分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.39,0:03:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!你的4分鐘、3分鐘2分鐘都跑哪去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是少女的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，欺人太甚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，不要阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你扔過去的話炸彈會．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你想怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了，你滾一邊去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了那我們先去防爆室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我忘了說一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦我爆炸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半徑兩公里之內的東西都會蒸發掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個該不會是．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不可能吧．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多要開始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是說不定．．．說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間移動，瞬間移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間移動，瞬間移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來．．．了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.71,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼停下來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我們和竹輪的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，梅爾優他們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，敵人逐漸消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間移動，瞬間移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前些時候的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被各位打得落花流水的敵國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然派了一群人來向我們道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.28,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好不容易戰爭就要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來你們最喜歡的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，」那個」是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛，那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的」這個那個」到底是什麼啦中校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，他還有脈搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，進行人工呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴對嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴對嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹嘛跑開?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家會嫁不出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別鬧了這關係到一條人命耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你幫他做不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋想想別的辦法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不想幫他做人工呼吸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救中校的新方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，有什麼辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，例如拿蔥卷在他的脖子上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要說這個的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放顆酸梅在額頭上，如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是把沙丁魚頭放在額頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後加以膜拜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，這是治療感冒的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，那其它呢?還有沒有什麼辦法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白飯不要咬，直接吞下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚嚇他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在手上寫一個」人」字然後吞10次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.33,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，香草，大家都很認真在想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在吃什麼竹輪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，你幹嘛吃竹輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中間是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就不會碰到嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣也通得過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很安全喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以各位，等打倒眼前的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡過這次的危機之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有各位最喜歡的這個和那個還有那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都免費贈送一年份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣，我們成功完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.15,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎接戰爭結束的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等協約簽訂後戰爭就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡不過，我還是無法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發給終結戰爭英雄的禮物居然是一年份的竹輪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我們一年份的竹輪，到底要我們怎麼用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有用啊，可以拿來當作竹輪型印章盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.21,0:07:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，你拿的那個不就是簽訂停戰協約的印章嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.35,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對喔！我忘了把印章拿給提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.52,0:08:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下慘了，據說對方是最重視禮儀的戰鬥部族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.63,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘記帶印章來的事萬一被發現的話．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要開戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿印章去給提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛阻止我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然要阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方可是很重視禮儀的部族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要拿印章過去也不能被發現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要怎麼拿過去呢?在這樣眾目睽睽之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.68,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要把它吹過去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪不是拿來這樣用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種情況下使用竹輪的確是有點困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方對於協約的內容已經確認同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來進行簽名蓋章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曇花一現的和平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.95,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提督想用竹輪代替印章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，這個主意棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶，竹輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來總算順利完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都是竹輪的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吹這個笛子的意思是把大家都殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(外星語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，他在生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.76,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這個世界沒那麼好混，光靠竹輪就想解決所有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心電感應，心電感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(其實是我把印章搞丟了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(這一切都是我的錯，對不起．．．)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(什麼!你這個笨蛋插花女!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算誠實去道歉也沒用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直是火上加油嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是剛才那個畫面有很多地方能讓人吐槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻呼哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.02,0:10:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣，多虧有竹輪才得以順利簽訂和平條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我們也變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有竹輪，什麼都辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有竹輪任何逆境都能克服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.73,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣我們跟竹輪成了不可分離的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是天使隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，請你們消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們已經玩完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就很難說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是無敵的天使隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為現在的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.03,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個?那個是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，你想知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是創造了無數奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救我們脫離無數危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個竹輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，那是竹輪麩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹輪永遠不滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始羅，剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被媒體發現熱戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被媒體發現熱戀是天大的紼聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剪刀和石頭也感到動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是對於布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面上看起來像是個迷糊蛋大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實這種類型最危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.67,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在打什麼算盤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊，那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了蛋糕要不要一起來吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?蛋糕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#04友情魚肉片試吃價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草莓奶油蛋糕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，我特地做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是天使隊的人都出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊成員的梅爾優居然請我吃蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一定是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那裏有一隻蝴蝶在飛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒藥反應，無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥及爆炸物反應，無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細菌和生化武器的痕跡也找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，那是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶 可能是牛肉罐頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，請喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是這杯紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這杯茶裏一定有劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，快點吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會被她殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，張開嘴巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我的不孝比你們先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲這十七年來一直體弱多病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有做過一件好事．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道怎麼樣?千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，你喜歡吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，還有很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為大家的份我都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，這些全都要吃完喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，這些全都要吃完喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有一種幸福的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是耍這種招數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然相信天使隊的笨蛋成員我實在太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，那個蛋糕真的好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定那個梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以成為我真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖這麼說但她畢竟是天使隊的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能那麼輕易就相信她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.56,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有什麼辦法可以確認梅爾優是不是真的想跟我做朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要開始羅，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬肉切片，豬肉切片，我愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，突然頭暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.08,0:15:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，梅爾優居然奮不顧身的衝出來救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然懷疑她，實在是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨死了，笨死了，笨死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.06,0:15:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到會在那裏撞上電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不相信任何人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，我記得她說今天要做起司蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，她怎麼可能故意把我扔去給電車撞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是答應我要跟我一起吃起司蛋糕嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已經往生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我這種生病專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓心臟停個幾秒鐘根本就是小事一樁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的死，你真的很傷心啊梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你的心裏原來這麼有份量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.15,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我居然那樣惡毒地測試你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了，千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，你怎麼死掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易進來了一個好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我真的會死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超魔術，掙脫大成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，原來你還活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，你按的是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，不要按啊為什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(一個月後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我．．．我還以為我死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然把我活生生的射出宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下你的狐貍尾巴終於露出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優·櫻葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要一起來吃蘋果派啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘋果派的花語是友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.19,0:17:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優難道你真的把我當好朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你自己撞過來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底出了什麼事?千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼打扮成這個樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉哩囉嗦的吵死了快點向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.15,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我向你道歉可是究竟要道什麼歉呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，聽得見聲音卻看不見人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，因為你太矮了所以我沒看見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.53,0:17:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，還有那邊的老太婆妝畫的還真濃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我是老太婆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，梅爾優，救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到天使隊的人在欺負我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優一定會出面救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?為什麼香草會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優出去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震驚．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不論發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不再相信梅爾優·櫻葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?千歲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.22,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，那傢伙一邊找大家麻煩一邊在找你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟她之間發生了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定千歲是希望梅爾優能陪她玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.65,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很笨耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是她想跟你做朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟千歲本來就是朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，你是怎麼了?怎麼這樣一身狼狽呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，因為發生了一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.07,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，我剛才做了泡芙等一下要不要一起吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優是曾出現在我夢中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.45,0:18:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟真正的朋友起這樣開心的逛廟會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我連想都沒想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在正在享受有生以來第一次的幸福滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我總覺得好像少了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對對，就是這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是高興的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，快點逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.01,0:19:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，你不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小傷算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我們兩人友情的威力來殲滅敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.22,0:20:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我們兩人友情的威力來殲滅敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，請看這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.39,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是新型的擴散能源炮現在是試用期間大優惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝在梅爾優的機體土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然外形好像沒什麼變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那我就趕快來試用看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.13,0:20:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?千歲呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(三個月後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫烏丸千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也為了追求真正的友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷失於戰場的可憐女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找了你好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅．．．梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，跟我一起回去托朗斯巴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能跟你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟你在一起我就會很不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千歲，把自己的不幸怪罪到別人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是鐵證如山的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.92,0:21:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這麼說我們不是好朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯吧，千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人．．．你這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.17,0:21:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.59,0:21:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你們救了我嗎?
